Otyebis Staff:



The soldiers stopped at a hallway.  One of the soldiers turned to Khonkolor.  
"Matches are still going on, so we don't know who you shall be fighting.  Hot 
Rod and Epyon both won their matches so they should be near by.  We will 
allow you to use your comm. system to communicate them.  These hallways lead 
to your quarters, an area to be repaired and recharged, etc."

The soldiers walked away.
